    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the robust 3.8L 9A1 power plant with Direct Fuel Injection. This naturally aspirated flat-six delivers a linear power band and is mated to a lightning-fast 7-speed PDK dual-clutch transmission. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing adaptive damping for surgical turn-in and lateral stability. Every factory VIN sticker remains intact, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation or fluid seepage. Maintenance is up-to-date with recent PDK service and brake fluid flush. This is a collector-grade example of the final hydraulic-steering 911, offering unparalleled mechanical feedback and analog soul.",
